<paragraph blockId="14.[2706,3504,3123,3689]" lastBlockId="14.[1883,3504,3702,4637]" pageId="14" pageNumber="363">Assignments of subspecies is based on morphological analysis of G. H. H. Tate and R. Archbold in 1939 and molecular analysis of D. J. Colgan and S. Soheili in 2008, but some affiliations are surmised based on geographical proximity. Additional molecular studies are needed to fully clarify subspecific taxonomy. Three subspecies recognized.</paragraph>
